            "sourceIds": [
              "legacy:hundberget"
            ]
          },
          "body": {
            "text": "A scene from the film Jägarna was shot here. The couple sat cuddling at the top of what is known as Kärleksklippan. Local young people often hold parties at the top of the crag.\n\nIn English: Vertical, crimpy routes.",
            "method": "llm",
            "model": "gpt-5.6-sol",
            "sourceIds": [
              "legacy:hundberget"
            ]
          }
        },
        "directions": {
          "title": {
            "text": "Directions",
            "method": "llm",
            "model": "gpt-5.6-sol",
            "sourceIds": [
              "legacy:hundberget"
            ]
          },
          "body": {
            "text": "From the junction of roads 374 and 94, drive another kilometre to a car park directly beneath the crag. The sport climbing is not on the large wall, but on small crags scattered across the top of the hill.",
            "method": "llm",
            "model": "gpt-5.6-sol",
            "sourceIds": [
              "legacy:hundberget"
            ]
          }
